"Dufour,"  he  corrected. 

"Very  well — Dufour.  Is  this  enough  now?" 

"No,"  he  said.  "These  proofs  prove  nothing.  If  I 
am  dreaming  you,  it's  natural  that  you  know  what 
I  know.  Your  catalog,  for  all  its  length,  is  com- 
