of  bulletins,  and  of  theater  programs.  Everything 


44 


gives  witness,  he  had  said.  Nierenstein  backed 
him;  don  Alejandro,  "after  three  resounding  Sat- 
urdays" (as  Irala  put  it),  approved  the  motion. 
Nora  Erfjord  had  resigned  her  position  as  secre- 
